resourceAbstractObject.default: Data from the 'Marine and lagoon biodiversity' (BIOMARLA): Monitoring of pelagic or benthic marine and lagoon communities. This observatory is part of the Montpellier Research Observatory of Environment (OSU OREME, oreme.org). It consists in different observing tasks: Coralligenous reefs ; Marine planktonic communities ; Phytoplankton pictures ; Thau microbial communities.
